# camera RAW formats — never committed.
# Photos enter the repo only after passing through scripts/prep-photo.sh,
# which produces a 3000px sRGB JPEG with EXIF stripped (incl. GPS).
# Committing the raw originals would defeat the resize, balloon repo
# size, and risk leaking location metadata.
*.CR2
*.CR3
*.NEF
*.ARW
*.RAF
*.ORF
*.RW2
*.DNG

# iPhone HEIC — same logic. Always export to JPEG via prep-photo.sh.
*.HEIC
*.heic

# General-purpose escape hatch: any file marked "-original" in its name
# is treated as a non-shippable source. Use this naming convention when
# keeping the original alongside a processed copy locally during a
# Lightroom-equivalent workflow.
*-original.*
